('Food Recommendation System ',5051,'rrrrrrrr-rrrr-rrrr-rrrr-rrrrrrrrrrrr','Tourist or lifelong resident, people in Singapore enjoy sampling its numerous cuisines. However, even the most adventurous people have some limitations to what flavours they like, ways in which their diets must be restricted and other food related preferences. Our system helps people choose something to eat without having them go through the names and images of unfamiliar dishes. This is achieved by asking the user a small number of pertinent questions, trying to determine the dish that best meets the user"s food preferences 窶� Looking for something spicy? Something light? What meat do you want to eat?','http://media.tumblr.com/3f81fad6ef163759fff8077580d94752/tumblr_inline_nj4nxkE0C21qersu1.png','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MYZfjfkwRII');
